articles.title: Texas Tech uses late TD to end perfect ISU start - ESPN
articles.description: Behren Morton drove Texas Tech 71 yards for the winning touchdown with 20 seconds left, and the Red Raiders denied No. 11 Iowa State its best start in program history with a 23-22 upset Saturday.
